The course introduces the concepts in pedagogy, the problems of didactics, the theories of education, the principles of arranging pedagogical process and planning the study; the role of pedagogue (properties, purification, communication skills); methods of learning and teaching; the history of pedagogy; educational system and adjustment.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to give an overview of: * the main concepts in pedagogy and didactics, basis and theories; * the history of pedagogy; * the conditions, the influences and the problems of education; * the role of pedagogue; * an arrangement of pedagogical process; * an educational system and adjustments.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Student knows the concepts and the principles of pedagogy and education.
* Student knows the history of education and different approaches.
* Student understands the role of pedagogue.
* Student knows an educational adjustments.
